  "\\textit{Provenance note:} P5 percentage values are computed from the March 4, 2025",
  "run in \\texttt{planted\\_exps/p5\\_series}, generated by Claude Code. An earlier",
  "Claude Code run (March 1, 2025, \\texttt{claude\\_p5\\_ps5/}) covers the Reference",
  "condition only. The P5 series appears to have been regenerated between these dates",
